    <title>Hello Hexo</title>
    <url>/2019/10/27/Hello-Hexo/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>This is my first attempt at writing a blog.<br>个人练习/学习用，不具参考意义, 实际还需自行验证看实际渲染效果</p>
</blockquote>
<a id="more"></a>

<h3 id="Hexo-Markdown-Practise"><a href="#Hexo-Markdown-Practise" class="headerlink" title="Hexo Markdown Practise"></a>Hexo Markdown Practise</h3><h4 id="标题"><a href="#标题" class="headerlink" title="标题"></a>标题</h4><figure class="highlight clean"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">#       h1  </span><br><span class="line">##      h2  </span><br><span class="line">---  </span><br><span class="line">######  h6</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><span>效果如下:</span><br>#h1<br>##h2<br>######h6</p>
<hr>
<h4 id="斜-粗体"><a href="#斜-粗体" class="headerlink" title="斜/粗体"></a>斜/粗体</h4><figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="strong">*斜体*</span></span><br><span class="line">*<span class="strong">*加粗*</span><span class="strong">*</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="strong">*</span>*<span class="strong">*斜体加粗*</span>*<span class="strong">*</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><span>效果如下:</span><br><em>斜体</em><br><strong>加粗</strong><br><strong><em>斜体加粗</em></strong>  </p>
<hr>
<h4 id="下划线"><a href="#下划线" class="headerlink" title="下划线"></a>下划线</h4><figure class="highlight gcode"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">*** <span class="comment">(三个以上星号)</span></span><br><span class="line">--- <span class="comment">(三个以上横线)</span></span><br><span class="line">___ <span class="comment">(三个以上下划线)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><span>效果如下:</span>  </p>
<hr>
<hr>
<hr>
<h4 id="删除线"><a href="#删除线" class="headerlink" title="删除线"></a>删除线</h4><figure class="highlight haml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">~~我是删除线~~</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><span>效果如下:</span><br><del>我是删除线</del></p>
<hr>
<h4 id="链接文字-图片"><a href="#链接文字-图片" class="headerlink" title="链接文字/图片"></a>链接文字/图片</h4><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[<span class="string">超链接名</span>](<span class="link">超链接地址 "超链接title"</span>)</span><br><span class="line">![<span class="string">图片alt</span>](<span class="link">图片地址 "图片title"</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">[<span class="string">必应</span>](<span class="link">//www.bing.com/ "我是必应"</span>)</span><br><span class="line">![<span class="string">头像</span>](<span class="link">//image/my_avatar.jpg "我是一只狗"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><span>效果如下:</span><br><a href="//www.bing.com/" title="我是必应">必应</a><br><img src="/images/my_avatar.jpg" alt="头像" title="我是一只狗"></p>
<hr>
<h4 id="代码片段-代码块"><a href="#代码片段-代码块" class="headerlink" title="代码片段/代码块"></a>代码片段/代码块</h4><figure class="highlight scilab"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[代码片段]</span><br><span class="line">&lt;code&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="title">hello</span><span class="params">()</span>&#123;  </span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">printf</span>(<span class="string">"hello\n"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;  </span><br><span class="line">&lt;code&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight autohotkey"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[代码块]</span><br><span class="line">```python</span><br><span class="line">#!/usr/bin/python</span><br><span class="line">print(<span class="string">"life is short!"</span>)</span><br><span class="line">```</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><span>效果如下:</span><br><code><br>function hello(){<br>  printf("hello\n");<br>}<br></code></p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#!/usr/bin/python</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">print</span> <span class="string">'life is short!'</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<hr>
<h4 id="表格"><a href="#表格" class="headerlink" title="表格"></a>表格</h4><figure class="highlight gherkin"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">列1    |<span class="string"> 列2  </span>|<span class="string"> 列3  </span>|<span class="string"> 列4  </span>|<span class="string"> 列5</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">-----  </span>|<span class="string"> :--- </span>|<span class="string"> ---: </span>|<span class="string"> :--: </span>|<span class="string"> --</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">Line1  </span>|<span class="string"> 12   </span>|<span class="string"> 34   </span>|<span class="string"> 56   </span>|<span class="string"> 78</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">Line2  </span>|<span class="string"> 123  </span>|<span class="string"> 345  </span>|<span class="string"> 567  </span>|<span class="string"> 789</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">Line3  </span>|<span class="string"> 1234 </span>|<span class="string"> 3456 </span>|<span class="string"> 5678 </span>|<span class="string"> 789A</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><span>效果如下:</span>  </p>
